hopobject.body: Special Delivery hr.top-steroids-online.com Based in London, England, Splash Damage(R) Ltd is an independently-owned developer dedicated to AAA multiplayer experiences. The studio most recently created the acclaimed worldwide #1 hit RAD Soldiers(R) for iPhone and iPad, and the worldwide #1 best-seller BRINK(TM) for Xbox 360(R), PlayStation(R)3 and PC. Splash Damage previously developed the popular Enemy Territory franchise for id Software, including the world's first free-to-play shooter Wolfenstein: Enemy Territory(TM) and its PC sequel, the UK and US #1 hit Enemy Territory: QUAKE Wars(TM). The studio is currently developing Batman: Arkham Origins(TM) multiplayer and other projects.
